#. Tag: title
#: reference.docbook:14
#, no-c-format
msgid "Menus"
msgstr "Menu"

#. Tag: para
#: reference.docbook:16
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Below is a complete list of the menu selections in &kmymoney;, with a very "
"brief description of what each one does. Note that many of these menu "
"choices will be unavailable, or grayed out, depending on the current display "
"or state of the application. In addition, some may not be present if it "
"relates to a feature not included in your particular version. For example, "
"you are not able to edit an account unless you have an account selected or "
"displayed in the current view."
msgstr ""
"Segue un elenco completo delle opzioni del menu di &kmymoney;, con una breve "
"spiegazione della loro funzione. È bene notare che molte di queste opzioni "
"potrebbero non essere disponibili, o disabilitate, in base alla vista "
"corrente o allo stato dell'applicazione. Inoltre, alcune potrebbero non "
"essere presenti se si riferiscono a una funzionalità non inclusa nella tua "
"versione specifica. Ad esempio, non puoi modificare un conto a meno che tu "
"non abbia un conto selezionato o visualizzato nella vista corrente."

#. Tag: title
#: reference.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid "File Menu"
msgstr "Menu File"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: reference.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>New book</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Nuovo libro</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: reference.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Creates a new, empty &kmymoney; data file. Only one &kmymoney; file can be "
"open at once, so this will close your current file first, if one is open."
msgstr ""
"Crea un nuovo file di dati di &kmymoney; vuoto. È possibile aprire solo un "
"file &kmymoney; alla volta, quindi questa operazione chiuderà prima il file "
"attuale, se ce n'è uno aperto."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: reference.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Open</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Apri...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: reference.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens an existing &kmymoney; data file."
msgstr "Apre un file di dati esistente di &kmymoney;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: reference.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Open Recent</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Apri recente</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: reference.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid "Provides quick access to recently opened files."
msgstr "Fornisce un accesso rapido ai file aperti di recente."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: reference.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Open Database...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Apri database...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: reference.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens an existing database."
msgstr "Apre un database esistente."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: reference.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Salva</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: reference.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Saves the currently open file. Only enabled if there are any changes to save."
msgstr ""
"Salva il file attualmente aperto. Abilitato solo se ci sono modifiche da "
"salvare."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: reference.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save As...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Salva come...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: reference.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid "Saves the currently open file with a different filename."
msgstr "Salva il file aperto con un nome diverso."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: reference.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Import</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>...</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Importa</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: reference.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Imports financial data from other file types, such as QIF and &gnucash;, or "
"a template file of accounts and categories that can be used in setting up "
"new accounts."
msgstr ""
"Importa dati finanziari da altri tipi di file, come QIF e &gnucash;, o un "
"modello di conti e categorie che può essere usato nella configurazione di "
"nuovi conti."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: reference.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Export</guimenuitem> <guimenuitem>...</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Esporta</guimenuitem> <guimenuitem>...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: reference.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Exports the current file as a different file type, such as QIF, or exports a "
"list of your accounts and categories as a template."
msgstr ""
"Esporta il file corrente come un tipo di file diverso, ad esempio QIF, "
"oppure esporta un elenco dei tuoi conti e categorie come modello."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: reference.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Print...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Stampa...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: reference.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid "Prints the current file."
msgstr "Stampa il file corrente."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: reference.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Backup...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Copia di sicurezza...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: reference.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid "Saves a backup the current file."
msgstr "Salva una copia di sicurezza del file corrente."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: reference.docbook:152
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Personal Data...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Dati personali...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: reference.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid "Allows to edit personal data."
msgstr "Permette di modificare i dati personali."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: reference.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>File information...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Informazioni sul file...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: reference.docbook:165
#, no-c-format
msgid "Displays information about the currently open &kmymoney; file."
msgstr "Visualizza informazioni sul file aperto di &kmymoney;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: reference.docbook:170
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>W</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Close</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>W</keycap> </keycombo> </"
"shortcut><guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Chiudi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: reference.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid "Closes the currently open data file."
msgstr "Chiude il file di dati attualmente aperto."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: reference.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Esci</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: reference.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Quits &kmymoney;. Offers to save the currently open data file, if there are "
"any changes."
msgstr ""
"Esce da &kmymoney;. Offre la possibilità di salvare il file di dati "
"attualmente aperto, se ci sono modifiche."

#. Tag: title
#: reference.docbook:198
#, no-c-format
msgid "Edit Menu"
msgstr "Menu Modifica"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: reference.docbook:201
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Undo</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Modifica</guimenu><guimenuitem>Annulla</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: reference.docbook:208
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reverses the most recent action."
msgstr "Annulla l'azione più recente."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: reference.docbook:215
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Redo</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Modifica</guimenu><guimenuitem>Rifai</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: reference.docbook:222
#, no-c-format
msgid "Re-applies the most recently undone action."
msgstr "Riapplica l'azione annullata più di recente."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: reference.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Find transaction...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Modifica</guimenu><guimenuitem>Trova transazione...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: reference.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid "Searches transactions."
msgstr "Cerca le transazioni."

#. Tag: title
#: reference.docbook:242
#, no-c-format
msgid "View Menu"
msgstr "Menu Visualizza"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: reference.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>T</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Transaction Detail</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>T</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Visualizza</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Visualizza dettagli transazione..."
"</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: reference.docbook:253
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Shows transaction details in the <link linkend=\"details.ledgers\">Ledgers</"
"link> View. With this option turned on, all lines of the transaction will be "
"shown. When it is turned off, only one line will be shown."
msgstr ""
"Mostra i dettagli della transazione nella vista <link linkend=\"details."
"ledgers\">Registri</link>. Abilitando questa opzione, tutte le righe della "
"transazione saranno mostrate. Disabilitandola, sarà visualizzata solo una "
"riga."

#. Tag: para
#: reference.docbook:259
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you only want to see details for the currently selected transaction, but "
"only one line for the others, you can turn on the <link linkend=\"details."
"settings.register.lens\">Ledger Lens</link>."
msgstr ""
"Se vuoi vedere tutti i dettagli della transazione selezionata, ma solo una "
"linea per gli altri, puoi abilitare la <link linkend=\"details.settings."
"register.lens\">Lente del registro</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: reference.docbook:268
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Hide reconciled transactions</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Visualizza</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nascondi transazioni "
"riconciliate</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: reference.docbook:276
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hides reconciled transactions in the ledger."
msgstr "Nasconde le transazioni riconciliate nel registro."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: reference.docbook:281
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>U</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Hide unused categories</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>U</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Visualizza</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nascondi categorie inutilizzate</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: reference.docbook:289
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hides unused categories in the views."
msgstr "Nasconde dalle viste le categorie non utilizzate."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: reference.docbook:294
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show all accounts</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Visualizza</guimenu><guimenuitem>Mostra tutti i conti</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: reference.docbook:301
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Shows all accounts in the views, including closed accounts and accounts with "
"zero balance."
msgstr ""
"Mostra tutti i conti nelle viste, compresi i conti chiusi e quelli con saldo "
"pari a zero."

